<% title = 'SATrack | Home'; %>
<section class="landing-hero">
  <h1 class="landing-headline">SAT Prep Tool That <br> Actually Sticks</h1>
  <p class="landing-sub">Mnemonics you'll remember. Questions that adapt to you. Progress you can see. No subscriptions, no paywalls. 100% Free for students.</p>
  <div class="landing-cta">
    <a href="/auth/signup" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Start Studying Free</a>
    <a href="/vocab" class="btn-secondary btn-lg">Browse Words</a>
  </div>

</section>

<section class="social-proof">
  <div class="social-proof-stats">
    <div class="stat-block">
      <div class="stat-number">
        <%= stats.totalWords %>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-label">Words Generated</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-block">
      <div class="stat-number">
        <%= stats.totalQuestions %>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-label">Questions Answered</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-block">
      <div class="stat-number">
        <%= stats.totalUsers %>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-label">Active Users</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="social-proof-quotes">
    <p class="quote">"The mnemonics actually stick. I remembered words weeks later without reviewing."</p>
    <p class="quote">"Finally, an SAT tool that doesn't feel like a chore. The adaptive practice knows exactly where I'm weak."</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="demo-section">
  <h2>Try It Right Now</h2>
  <p class="demo-section-sub">
    Enter any SAT word to see what SATrack generates.
  </p>
  <form method="GET" action="/vocab" class="demo-search-wrap">
    <input type="text" name="word" placeholder="e.g., perspicacious" required>
    <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Look Up</button>
  </form>
  <div class="feature-section">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h3>Vocabulary That Stays With You</h3>
      <p>Every word gets a mnemonic device, a picture story, and an example sentence. Generated with AI + RAG so each entry feels authentic, not robotic. Rate entries and the system learns from your feedback. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-visual">Words</div>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-section feature-section--reverse">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h3>Practice Like the Real Test</h3>
      <p>Real College Board questions plus AI-generated ones styled after the official bank. The Bluebook interface feels exactly like test day. Adaptive mode targets your weakest topics automatically.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-visual">Practice</div>
  </div>
  <div class="feature-section">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h3>Never Forget a Word</h3>
      <p>Spaced repetition flashcards powered by the SM-2 algorithm. Cards you struggle with appear more often. Cards you know fade into the background. Just like Anki, built right in.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-visual">Flashcards</div>
  </div>
</section>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>